<h2 #travel-help>Travel Types

<p>
  The travel type is a broad description of how you intend to travel the Camino.
  The type is used to estimate the amount of time it will take you to walk a (possibly hilly) segment of the way.
  The type is also used to help provide defaults for the sort of services you might need along the way and the daily distance traveled.
  Generally, people either walk or use a bicycle.

<table .table .table-striped>
  <caption>Travel Types
  <thead>
    <tr>
