            This is the default travel type.
    <tr>
        <td>^{caminoTravelIcon Walking_Naismith}
        <td>_{caminoTravelMsg Walking_Naismith}
        <td>Walking the Camino for powerful walkers.
            This option uses a rule to calculate the time taken to travel a given distance
